01:29:48.702 --> 01:29:52.738
Keep pressing.
- So let me ask you one more time, General Lu Tong...

01:29:52.740 --> 01:29:55.711
will you take responsibility for the
human rights abuses...

01:29:55.835 --> 01:29:57.671
