01:30:04.627 --> 01:30:07.080
Can't, or won't, Lu Tong?

01:30:07.180 --> 01:30:09.480
- Can't, or won't, General Lu Tong?

01:30:09.482 --> 01:30:12.327
On balance, I'd suggest "can't", considering

01:30:12.327 --> 01:30:15.127
I've just found General Lu Tong in the lobby,

01:30:15.129 --> 01:30:17.802
and his chauffeur is currently
live on air answering

01:30:17.802 --> 01:30:20.402
questions about Far Eastern geopolitics.

01:30:20.404 --> 01:30:24.095
No? Any comments you want to make
about the use of sexual torture...

01:30:24.097 --> 01:30:25.454
by your own military?

01:30:26.547 --> 01:30:30.990
Ask him about London traffic.
- London traffic, General Lu Tong,

01:30:30.992 --> 01:30:35.009
